Not the greatest of thrillers from the description i read when i first considered buying this movie, the cover sleeve got my attention first. However it was a decent purchase, not a bad movie with some cool twists and good looking ladies. Worth it.

This film is a thriller with a twist. The picture on the box has absolutely nothing to do with the film's story line. Its a story of how a woman and her boyfriend conspire to kill the anal retentive husband of her friend. Of course theres a plot twist. But this film by no means is sleazy, like it's cover. And speaking of the cover....who are these women? They're not in the film.
